 different scenarios such as variable record sizes, different\ndistributions of join attributes, and different storage types, including HDD,\nSSD, and Amazon Elastic Block Store (Amazon EBS).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Dec 2021 05:55:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-07"}
